articles.author: Nicolás Misculin
articles.title: Argentina heads to the polls in grip of fierce economic crisis - Reuters
articles.description: Argentines headed to the polls on Sunday to vote in a general election under the shadow of the South American country's worst economic crisis in two decades, which has driven the rise of an outsider far-right libertarian who is in pole position to win.
